			<CASNumber>140-89-6</CASNumber>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Xanthate usually refers to a salt of xanthic acid. It also refers to the anion [R−O−CS2]− and may refer to an ester of xanthic acid. Xanthate is a flotation collector of sulfide ore. Its chemical name is xanthate or alkyl dithiocarbonate. Much of the xanthate use is in flotation systems, where selectivity between sulfide minerals is not an issue and the goal is to recover most of the sulfides and precious metal values.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">黄原酸盐通常指黄原酸的盐。它还指阴离子[R-O-CS2]-，也可指黄原酸的酯。黄原酸盐是硫化矿的一种浮选捕收剂。其化学名称为黄原酸盐或烷基二硫代碳酸酯。黄原酸盐主要用于浮选系统，在这种系统中，硫化矿物之间的选择性不是问题，目标是回收大部分硫化物和贵金属价值。</common:generalComment>
